        <header>
          <h1>The Ultimate Multiplayer Snake Experience</h1>
          <p>Play <a href="/game">Snake Online</a> on iOS and Android. Compete globally, earn <a href="/tokenomics">MXR tokens</a>, and join our <a href="/play-to-earn">play-to-earn gaming ecosystem</a>.</p>
