        <section>
          <h2>MXR Token Presale</h2>
          <p>Join the <a href="/presale">MXR Token presale</a> and be part of the Snake Online gaming revolution. MXR is a Solana SPL utility token powering our gaming ecosystem with fast transactions and low fees. Read our <a href="/whitepaper">whitepaper</a> to learn more.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Stage 1: $0.075 per MXR - 67% discount</li>
            <li>Stage 2: $0.15 per MXR - 40% discount</li>
            <li>Stage 3: $0.25 per MXR - Final price</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Total Supply: 1,000,000,000 MXR tokens on Solana blockchain. See full <a href="/tokenomics">tokenomics details</a>.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2>About Snake Online</h2>
          <p><a href="/game">Snake Online</a> is a real, playable mobile game available now on iOS App Store and Google Play. <a href="/download">Download now</a> to start playing!</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Real-time multiplayer battles with players worldwide - see the <a href="/leaderboard">global leaderboard</a></li>
            <li>Compete for rankings and climb the <a href="/leaderboard">leaderboards</a></li>
            <li>Daily challenges and rewards</li>
            <li>Custom snake skins and cosmetics</li>
            <li><a href="/play-to-earn">Play-to-earn mechanics</a> with MXR tokens</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Learn more about <a href="/game-features">game features</a> and <a href="/about">our team</a>.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2>Why Choose MXR Token?</h2>
          <p>MXR Token is built on Solana for speed and efficiency. Use MXR for in-game purchases, tournament entries, governance voting, and earning rewards through gameplay. MiCA-compliant utility token with real use cases. Read our <a href="/whitepaper">whitepaper</a> and check the <a href="/roadmap">development roadmap</a>.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2>How to Buy MXR Tokens</h2>
          <p>Visit our <a href="/presale">presale page</a> to purchase MXR tokens:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Get a Solana wallet like Phantom or Solflare - see our <a href="/need-help/wallet-connection">wallet guide</a></li>
            <li>Purchase SOL on your preferred exchange</li>
            <li>Connect your wallet to our <a href="/presale">presale page</a></li>
            <li>Select amount and complete your purchase</li>
          </ol>
          <p>Need help? Visit our <a href="/help">help center</a> or <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
        </section>
        
